data.description: Welcome to the Sugarmill Woods Cypress Village community! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence sounds like a fantastic place to call home. Here's a breakdown of the key features and highlights: Location: The community is surrounded by beautiful greenery and offers a highly sought-after lifestyle. Being situated on the first fairway of the golf course adds to the appeal for golf enthusiasts. Garage: The attached single-car garage is a practical feature, providing protection for your vehicle from the elements. Living Space: The combined dining and living areas create an open and inviting space, perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. Kitchen: A well-appointed kitchen with plenty of cabinet space is essential for any home, making meal preparation and storage convenient. Tranquil Backyard: The backyard offers a peaceful retreat, ideal for enjoying morning coffee or relaxing in the evenings while embracing the Florida lifestyle. Community Amenities: The community seems to offer a wide range of amenities, catering to various interests. Whether it's golf, tennis, fitness, Residents have access to a fabulous lifestyle right within their neighborhood. Convenience: The prime location of this home is a significant advantage, with nearby shopping centers, dining options, parks, and excellent schools, making daily life more convenient and enjoyable. Accessibility: The proximity to major highways ensures easy travel to nearby cities and attractions, which is a valuable feature for those who like to explore beyond the immediate neighborhood.  Located in Beautiful Homosassa, Fl.  You can enjoy the tranquility of the countryside while still having convenient access to modern amenities. Nearby, you'll find stores like Walmart, Publix, Dunkin Donuts, as well as the Suncoast Parkway and Tampa International Airport, which are less than an hour away. The location also offers various attractions and recreational opportunities. Sugarmill Country Club with its 18-hole golf course and restaurant, Homosassa River, 7 Sisters Springs, Chassahowitzka River, and several waterfront destinations like The Freezer Tiki Bar and Monkey Bar at Florida Cracker Riverside Resort are all within reach. State parks and wildlife management areas are also nearby, providing ample opportunities for outdoor activities.  This home is priced to sell! Great for the first-time buyer or empty nester.  Don't Wait!  Call now to make your appointment to see this home!  Hot Tub Sold separately, does not stay with the home.
